title: Compare Tr. of Vienna to Tr. of Versailles

content.question: Directions: In writing your essays, use specific examples to support your answer. The suggested writing time is 30 minutes. Compare and contrast the degree of success of treaties negotiated in Vienna (1814-1815) and Versailles (1919) in achieving European stability.
